metadata.name: T h e  V o i d
metadata.description:
In the duality in which she grew up, she tried to find herself, build herself piece by piece. 
She wanted to see the world with new eyes. She had to hide a particle of her being as she went on, and whenever she gained something, she lost something.That was what that culture taught her. 
In the culture that you don't get to speak, she will be the one that breaths fire and screams justice.
